OL,3,CMan charged following investigation
OL,4,Cinto fraud allegations at council
OL,6,FA man has been charged with fraud
OL,7,Fafter a police investigation into
OL,8,Fmalpractice at a council over eight
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FRichard Shaw, 45, will appear in court
OL,12,Fcharged with fraud by abuse of
OL,13,Fposition in relation to Bolton Council.
OL,15,FThe offences are alleged to have been
OL,16,Fcommitted between February 2015 and
OL,17,FApril 2023.
