OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,7,Fthe charge comes after a comprehensive
OL,8,Finvestigation by its Economic Crime
OL,9,FUnit.
OL,11,FDetective Sergeant Daniel Sanchez,
OL,12,Ffrom GMP, said: "We have worked
OL,13,Fcarefully through all information and
OL,14,Fevidence, from which we have now
OL,15,Fsecured a charge.
OL,17,F"Our team have remained in close
OL,18,Fcontact with the local authority, who
OL,19,Fhave assisted us throughout this
OL,20,Fprocess.
